OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782326890
OL,3,COne of UK's largest nursery chains
OL,4,Cserved with safeguarding notice
OL,6,FOfsted has served one of the largest
OL,7,Fnursery chains in the UK with a legal
OL,8,Fnotice over concerns that some of its
OL,9,Fsettings are not meeting safeguarding
OL,10,Fand welfare requirements.
OL,12,FBright Horizons, which has 247
OL,13,Fsettings across England, was served
OL,14,Fwith a Welfare Requirements Notice
OL,15,F(WRN) after checks between October
OL,16,F2025 and June 2026 highlighted
OL,17,F"significant weaknesses in
OL,18,Forganisational safeguarding
OL,19,Fleadership, governance, oversight and
OL,20,Fpractice" in some of its settings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
