OL,3,COne of UK's largest nursery chains
OL,4,Cserved with safeguarding notice
OL,6,FAccording to Ofsted, this is the first
OL,7,Ftime it has served this legal notice
OL,8,Fat the group level to a nursery chain.
OL,10,FOne of the chain's nurseries in north-
OL,11,Fwest London closed in May last year,
OL,12,Fafter its employee, Vincent Chan, was
OL,13,Ffound to have carried out numerous
OL,14,Fsexual offences, including child abuse.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
