OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782326890
OL,3,COne of UK's largest nursery chains
OL,4,Cserved with safeguarding notice
OL,6,FOfsted said it carried out regulatory
OL,7,Factivity across multiple Bright
OL,8,FHorizons Family Solutions Limited
OL,9,Fsettings nationally after it received
OL,10,F"concerns following a serious
OL,11,Fsafeguarding incident" from September
OL,12,F2025.
OL,14,FThis activity included "inspections,
OL,15,Fregulatory visits, regulatory
OL,16,Ftelephone calls and direct engagement
OL,17,Fwith senior leaders".
OL,19,FIt found breaches in 69 settings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
