OL,3,COne of UK's largest nursery chains
OL,4,Cserved with safeguarding notice
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIn its report, Ofsted highlighted
OL,12,Fseveral actions that providers were
OL,13,Frequired to take before 1 August.
OL,15,FThe report read: "These actions relate
OL,16,Fto organisational arrangements and do
OL,17,Fnot reflect concerns identified at
OL,18,Fevery individual setting.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
