PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782326890
OL,3,COne of UK's largest nursery chains
OL,4,Cserved with safeguarding notice
OL,6,F"The majority of settings continue to
OL,7,Fmeet requirements; however, the
OL,8,Fprovider has not demonstrated that it
OL,9,Fcan ensure safeguarding is
OL,10,Fconsistently effective across its
OL,11,Fprovision."
OL,13,FOfsted said it will continue to
OL,14,Fmonitor Bright Horizons and update
OL,15,Fprogress on its website as changes are
OL,16,Fmade.
OL,18,FITV News has reached out to Bright
OL,19,FHorizons UK for comment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
